OL,3,ETHE OPINIONATED PIGG``````````U`///{5n'
OL,4,                               U*~}|>
OL,5,B"Shove rust in my gob and     U8<;6
OL,6,Bpaint swear words on my back -Um}e/!'
OL,7,BI'm sick to death of everything this   
OL,8,Bweek. Yes - even THAT.                 
OL,10,F"The reason for this is because Live   
OL,11,Fand Kicking is back on television, and 
OL,12,Fwith it more banal game reviews.       
OL,14,B"Live and Kicking is watched by dozens 
OL,15,Bof children every week, and they'll all
OL,16,Bhappily nod at every uneducated comment
OL,17,Bmade by the young 'computer boy'       
OL,18,Bpresenting the regular games slot."    
