OL,5,B"I put out a call to the      U8<;6
OL,6,Bmakers of Live and Kicking,   Um}e/!'
OL,7,Band hope it reaches Zoe Ball's massive,
OL,8,Bdish-like ears: please, axe the child, 
OL,9,Band run a gaming strand which doesn't  
OL,10,Btreat gamesplayers like nerds. Your    
OL,11,Bcurrent slot is worthless.             
OL,13,F"Also, I request that Jamie Theakston  
OL,14,Fpresent the slot naked, because he has 
OL,15,Fa lovely lithe body.                   
OL,17,B"That is all."                         
